            <title>[SOLR-134] Handle Time values in fields correctly (UTC + ISO 8601)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-134</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a patch for automatically converting Time objects in fields to the UTC/ISO 8601 format that Solr can parse.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Which means this will work:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  connection.add(:id =&amp;gt; 1, :created_at =&amp;gt; Time.now)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
