                            <comment id="12469618" author="codahale" created="Thu, 1 Feb 2007 23:40:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Includes unit test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12469643" author="ehatcher" created="Fri, 2 Feb 2007 02:44:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;  1) Failure:&lt;br/&gt;
test_xml_date(FieldTest) &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;./test/unit/field_test.rb:27&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;&quot;&amp;lt;field name=&apos;what_time_should_we_party_as_if_it_is&apos;&amp;gt;1999-12-31T08:00:00Z&amp;lt;/field&amp;gt;&quot;&amp;gt; expected but was&lt;br/&gt;
